## Scheduling
- Stagger posts across platforms (don't post everywhere same day)
- Day 1: Primary platform (where original was posted)
- Day 2: Twitter/X + å³åˆ»
- Day 3: LinkedIn + Reddit
- Day 4: å°çº¢ä¹¦ (if translated)
- Day 5: Blog + email newsletter

## Quality Rules
- Each version must feel native to its platform
- Never copy-paste across platforms (algorithms penalize)
- Adapt, don't just translate
- Each version should be at least 40% different from original
- Preserve core message and CTA across all versions
